---
title: Chophouse Double Striploin and Creamy Mushrooms with Potatoes, Bacon and Green Onion Goat Cheese
description: This steakhouse dinner is simple, juicy and luxurious. Pan-seared steaks are smothered with delectable creamy mushrooms, and crisp roasted potatoes are topped with creamy green onion goat cheese and bacon. Snap peas bring a bit of green and finishes the plate perfectly.

